data.description: CDD is paid off totaling $39K! Are you interested in a new construction home but don’t want to go through the process of waiting for it to be built? Let me introduce you to 324 Sawgrass located in the highly desirable community of Wildlight! The Santa Fe floor plan was recently completed by Riverside Homes! This stunning property features 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, an extended primary bedroom, a Chef's kitchen with double ovens & quartz countertops, a fenced-in backyard that backs up to preserve, brick pavers in the front & rear of the home, a 3 car garage, & many more upgrades! The Wildlight community has so much to offer including a variety of amenities, a clubhouse, a community pool, a playground, and tennis courts. Located conveniently to I-95 and just a short drive to the beautiful beaches of Amelia Island! Don't miss your chance to own this brand-new home!
